00:39:03.900 --> 00:39:06.480 align:middle line:10%
>> I'm not talking about some
kind of pagan voodoo here.

00:39:06.480 --> 00:39:09.390 align:middle line:10%
I'm talking about something
real, something measurable

00:39:09.390 --> 00:39:10.840 align:middle line:10%
in the biology of the forest.

