00:39:22.550 --> 00:39:26.070 align:middle line:10%
And each tree has ten to
the fourth connections

00:39:26.070 --> 00:39:27.300 align:middle line:10%
to the trees around it.

00:39:27.300 --> 00:39:31.350 align:middle line:10%
And there are 10 to the
