everything as if it were.

00:45:23.790 --> 00:45:26.550 align:middle line:84%
>>WEIDNER: I tell
people that it's OK

00:45:26.550 --> 00:45:29.010 align:middle line:84%
if you want to call me
a conspiracy theorist,

00:45:29.010 --> 00:45:31.500 align:middle line:84%
but then I get to call you
a coincidence theorist.

00:45:31.500 --> 00:45:32.860 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Exactly.

